Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe Chairman/Executive of the National Drug Law Enforcement Agency, Brig. Gen. Mohamed Buba Marwa (Retd.) has lost his first wife.
A statement by the family on January 8, 2022, said Mrs Zainab Marwa died in the early hours of the day at 66.
She had been brief ill.
“The deceased is survived by four children; Abubakar, Mohamed Jr, Mariam and Zainab, and 10 grandchildren as well as her siblings and aged mother,” the statement said.
A burial arrangement will be announced at a later date by the family.
